							generally speaking?</label></li>
					<input type="range" name="16" id="16" min="1" max="5">
					<p id="16Output"></p>

					<!--Q17: LOOKING FOR VALIDATION THROUGH SOCIAL MEDIA-->
					<li><label for="17">How often do you look to seek validation from features of social media?</label>
					</li>
					<input type="range" name="17" id="17" min="1" max="5">
					<p id="17Output"></p>

					<!--Q18: FEELING DEPRESSED OR DOWN-->
